# CODEOWNERS file for Kronos - Distributed Selenium Grid
#
# This file defines code ownership for different parts of the repository.
# Code owners are automatically requested for review when pull requests
# are opened that modify files they own.
#
# GitHub will automatically request reviews from code owners when:
# 1. A pull request is opened that modifies owned files
# 2. Branch protection rules require code owner reviews
# 3. Someone explicitly requests a review from code owners
#
# Syntax Examples:
#   * @global-owner                    # All files
#   /docs/ @docs-team                  # Specific directory
#   *.js @frontend-team @security      # File pattern with multiple owners
#   /api/ @backend-team @api-lead      # Directory with team and individual
#
# More info: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

